Ahora básicamente lo hemos averiguado.

00:27:11.680 --> 00:27:14.440
La gente a cargo del negocio

00:27:14.480 --> 00:27:16.360
son Sha Fei, Bai Yifang,
y Jin Shengcai.

00:27:16.560 --> 00:27:17.960
